channel.title: [317][PI] Teleport Interfaces
channel.description: Ill just get right to it.. When ever i click a teleport before a different one, the last one i clicked teleports me there. I know it sounds confusing or i dont make sence but.. EX: I click city teleports.. After im done i click boss teleports If i clicked on one of the bosses it would teleport me to a city. Its really annoying... :/
